      "cookedHtml": "<p>The “update bubbles” on our boards changed from this:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/ba2ca93f0b8ed85126a4c6683cad1e852fa20053.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.34.41 PM\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/ba2ca93f0b8ed85126a4c6683cad1e852fa20053.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.34.41 PM\" width=\"368\" height=\"479\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.34.41 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">368×479 11 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>To this:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/d/3da256f41245cc9fde085af3dc6bb849a7f267ac.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.32.56 PM\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/d/3da256f41245cc9fde085af3dc6bb849a7f267ac_2_690x160.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.32.56 PM\" width=\"690\" height=\"160\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-03-17 at 9.32.56 PM</span><span class=\"informations\">1898×442 23.9 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Does anyone know how to bring back the bubbles with numbers that switch from blue to grey, etc.?</p>"
