      "id": 224620,
      "postNumber": 3,
      "createdAt": "2025-03-19T14:45:02.809Z",
      "author": "shirozayas (Shiro Zayas)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/graylyn\">@graylyn</a>,</p>\n<p>On the CRM product, the update section appears once you open the item’s card:</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/f/6fbbd0f275cd3325360b25ec6ce4b86dd80141cf.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/f/6fbbd0f275cd3325360b25ec6ce4b86dd80141cf.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"338\" height=\"170\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">338×170 5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<hr />\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/a/2a5ee5df08aafb533df2bb431acd65b3cb511bdf.png\" title=\"tempsnip\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/a/2a5ee5df08aafb533df2bb431acd65b3cb511bdf.png\" alt=\"tempsnip\" width=\"464\" height=\"329\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">tempsnip</span><span class=\"informations\">464×329 13.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>You can change what appears first when you click on the card button by setting the Updates view as board default:</strong><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/9/492559364a74df8fec70c1aad0d4b4ec9c480c0c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/4/9/492559364a74df8fec70c1aad0d4b4ec9c480c0c.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"263\" height=\"251\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">263×251 11.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>Bubbles only appear on reagular boards, not CRM boards.</strong><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/7/c709024b514cf1486a31ec10a9102c7e72271cdb.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/7/c709024b514cf1486a31ec10a9102c7e72271cdb.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"226\" height=\"106\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">226×106 3.98 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>I hope this helps!</p>"
